[144.301956, "o", "to justify the hardware purchase, and both use a one-time purchase monetization model for the physical device. Essential's story of failing to build platform defensibility вЂ”\u001b[33;268H never meaningf\r\n\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m  \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;185;192;171m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m    \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198mully differentiating from Android OEM competitors вЂ”\u001b[34;58H is directly analogous to the existential challenge a new game console faces against Sony, Microsoft, and Nintendo.                                                                                                              \r\n\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m  \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;185;192;171m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m  5 \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               "]
